title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Match 4' game
maintext:
OLYMPIA, Wash. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the Washington Lottery’s “Match 4” game were:
08-15-20-21
(eight, fifteen, twenty, twenty-one)
